{
  "conversations": [
    {
      "conversationId": "lady geist_paradox_convo02",
      "lines": [
        {
          "order": 1,
          "character": "Lady geist",
          "audioFile": "ghost_match_start_ghost_chrono_convo02_01",
          "audioUrl": "audio/ghost_match_start_ghost_chrono_convo02_01.mp3",
          "text": "You know I've been to the Paradox Museum last summer.",
          "duration": 3.175
        },
        {
          "order": 2,
          "character": "Paradox",
          "audioFile": "chrono_match_start_ghost_chrono_convo02_02",
          "audioUrl": "audio/chrono_match_start_ghost_chrono_convo02_02.mp3",
          "text": "Did you enjoy yourself?",
          "duration": 1.594
        },
        {
          "order": 3,
          "character": "Lady geist",
          "audioFile": "ghost_match_start_ghost_chrono_convo02_03",
          "audioUrl": "audio/ghost_match_start_ghost_chrono_convo02_03.mp3",
          "text": "I found it clich\u00e9 and overwrought.",
          "duration": 2.551
        },
        {
          "order": 4,
          "character": "Paradox",
          "audioFile": "chrono_match_start_ghost_chrono_convo02_04",
          "audioUrl": "audio/chrono_match_start_ghost_chrono_convo02_04.mp3",
          "text": "Excuse me?",
          "duration": 1.359
        },
        {
          "order": 5,
          "character": "Lady geist",
          "audioFile": "ghost_match_start_ghost_chrono_convo02_05",
          "audioUrl": "audio/ghost_match_start_ghost_chrono_convo02_05.mp3",
          "text": "It was a multimillion exhibition with the emotional depth of a 10th grader writing \"I will rage against conformity\" in their poetry unit of remidial english",
          "duration": 9.407
        },
        {
          "order": 6,
          "character": "Paradox",
          "audioFile": "chrono_match_start_ghost_chrono_convo02_06",
          "audioUrl": "audio/chrono_match_start_ghost_chrono_convo02_06.mp3",
          "text": "It had a Hellenistic bust of Homer",
          "duration": 2.549
        },
        {
          "order": 7,
          "character": "Lady geist",
          "audioFile": "ghost_match_start_ghost_chrono_convo02_07",
          "audioUrl": "audio/ghost_match_start_ghost_chrono_convo02_07.mp3",
          "text": "Homer is also overwrought",
          "duration": 2.527
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "conversationId": "lady geist_paradox_convo03",
      "lines": [
        {
          "order": 1,
          "character": "Lady geist",
          "audioFile": "ghost_match_start_ghost_chrono_convo03_01",
          "audioUrl": "audio/ghost_match_start_ghost_chrono_convo03_01.mp3",
          "text": "How often does your little social club gather",
          "duration": 2.981
        },
        {
          "order": 2,
          "character": "Paradox",
          "audioFile": "chrono_match_start_ghost_chrono_convo03_02",
          "audioUrl": "audio/chrono_match_start_ghost_chrono_convo03_02.mp3",
          "text": "A few times a year",
          "duration": 1.516
        },
        {
          "order": 3,
          "character": "Lady geist",
          "audioFile": "ghost_match_start_ghost_chrono_convo03_03",
          "audioUrl": "audio/ghost_match_start_ghost_chrono_convo03_03.mp3",
          "text": "I'm assuming your ilk like to brag about what they stole?",
          "duration": 3.455
        },
        {
          "order": 4,
          "character": "Paradox",
          "audioFile": "chrono_match_start_ghost_chrono_convo03_04",
          "audioUrl": "audio/chrono_match_start_ghost_chrono_convo03_04.mp3",
          "text": "We're a bunch of bored rich people, of course we brag about what we stole.",
          "duration": 4.728
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "conversationId": "paradox_seven_convo01",
      "lines": [
        {
          "order": 1,
          "character": "Seven",
          "audioFile": "gigawatt_match_start_gigawatt_chrono_convo01_01",
          "audioUrl": "audio/gigawatt_match_start_gigawatt_chrono_convo01_01.mp3",
          "text": "For all the might your organization wields, you waste it on publicity stunts.",
          "duration": 5.359
        },
        {
          "order": 2,
          "character": "Paradox",
          "audioFile": "chrono_match_start_gigawatt_chrono_convo01_02",
          "audioUrl": "audio/chrono_match_start_gigawatt_chrono_convo01_02.mp3",
          "text": "We don't need to explain ourselves to you.",
          "duration": 2.291
        },
        {
          "order": 3,
          "character": "Seven",
          "audioFile": "gigawatt_match_start_gigawatt_chrono_convo01_03",
          "audioUrl": "audio/gigawatt_match_start_gigawatt_chrono_convo01_03.mp3",
          "text": "I would settle for you explaining it to anyone.",
          "duration": 2.426
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}